<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; background-color: #f9f9f9; }
    .header { background-color: #27ae60; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0; }
    .content { background-color: white; padding: 20px; }
    .success-box { background-color: #d5f4e6; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #27ae60; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 3px; }
    .details { margin: 15px 0; }
    .detail-row { padding: 8px 0; }
    .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #27ae60; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 10px 5px 10px 0; }
    .footer { background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 15px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #777; border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>✅ Your Package Delivered!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi {{customerName}},</p>
      <p>Great news! Your package has been successfully delivered.</p>
      
      <div class="success-box">
        <h3>Delivery Confirmed</h3>
        <div class="details">
          <div class="detail-row">
            <strong>Tracking Number:</strong> {{trackingNumber}}
          </div>
          <div class="detail-row">
            <strong>Order Number:</strong> #{{orderNumber}}
          </div>
          <div class="detail-row">
            <strong>Courier:</strong> {{courierName}}
          </div>
          <div class="detail-row">
            <strong>Delivered On:</strong> {{deliveredDate}}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <p><strong>Thank You For Your Purchase!</strong></p>
      <p>We hope you're happy with your order. Your feedback helps us improve our service.</p>
      
      <p>
        <a href="{{feedbackUrl}}" class="button">Share Your Feedback</a>
        <a href="https://dentalkart.com/orders" class="button">View Order</a>
      </p>
      
      <p><strong>What's Next?</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Enjoy your products!</li>
        <li>If you have any questions or concerns, we're here to help</li>
        <li>Don't forget to leave a review on your order</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>Need help? <a href="https://dentalkart.com/support">Contact our support team</a></p>
      
      <p>Happy shopping!<br><strong>DentalKart Team</strong></p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{year}} DentalKart. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
